It should bring you to the following page:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"880v4","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4n23s","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"8m011","text":"Click on the job submission that contains the failed sample under the 'Submission' tile, and it will take you to a new page that shows a table. On this new page, click on the “LIST VIEW” tab and it will show the task(s) that failed (e.g. “read_QC_trim” as shown below), which is indicate by a red exclamation mark in a triangle under the “Links” tab.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c8pt5","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dn97i","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":2,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"5lref","text":"Click on the task that failed (e.g. “read_QC_trim” as shown below) and it will show the step(s) within the task that failed (e.g. fastqc_clean as shown below), which is indicated by a red exclamation mark in a triangle under the “Links” tab.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7onqe","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3tpqt","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":3,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"5fmri","text":"Move the mouse over the warning sign (red exclamation mark in a triangle) and you will see the error message. In this case the error message reads “Task read_QC_trim.fastqc_clean:NA:1 failed. Job exited without an error, exit code 0. PAPI error code 9. Please check the log file for more details:
